(𝐌𝐞𝐝𝐢𝐮𝐦:-only 1st question....)
Open Wireshark (after installing).
Click on Capture & then Interfaces.
Select any running Network (Microsoft, Realtek, Oracle etc.) & then click on Start.
Open Chrome & type " www.rrpryj.org " & click on Result.
Come Back to Wireshark.
Give Filter as "http" & then click on apply.
On left bottom console, (Expand) HyperText Transfer Protocol.
Click on " Host :- " & Right click on it then select "Apoly as column". 
Select any http packet.
Right click on it & Select "Follow TCP stream" 
Hex code will be generated. Show it as output. (Host name).
